{"type":"message-part","messageId":"4b48d041-1be9-4d7d-b90f-3f08e177c762","role":"assistant","index":14,"part":{"type":"tool-attemptCompletion","toolCallId":"1EdXo5yHqtdSWjMg","state":"input-streaming","input":{"result":"I have created the `save_teams_token.sh` script at `/home/user/magicbell-task/save_teams_token.sh` and ensured it has execute permissions. I also saved a copy to `/logs/artifacts/code/save_teams_token.sh`.\n\n### Script Details:\n- **Usage**: `./save_teams_token.sh <USER_JWT> <WEBHOOK_URL>`\n- **Endpoint**: `PUT /channels/teams/tokens`\n- **Base URL**: `https://api.magicbell.com/v2` (can be overridden via `MAGICBELL_API_URL` environment variable)\n- **Payload**: `{\"webhook\": {\"url\": \"<WEBHOOK_URL>\"}}`\n- **Authentication**: Uses `Authorization: Bearer <USER_JWT>` header.\n\n### Script Content:\n```bash\n#!/bin/bash\n\n# Exit non-zero if arguments are missing\nif [ \"$#\" -ne 2 ]; then\n    echo \"Usage: $0 <USER_JWT> <WEBHOOK_URL>\"\n    exit 1\nfi\n\nUSER_JWT=$1\nWEBHOOK_URL=$2\n\n# Use MAGICBELL_API_URL if set, otherwise use default\nAPI_URL=${MAGICBELL_API_URL:-\"https://api.magicbell.com/v2\"}\n\n# Construct JSON payload\nPAYLOAD=$(cat <<EOF\n{\n  \"webhook\": {\n    \"url\": \"$WEBHOOK_URL\"\n  }\n}\nEOF\n)\n\n# Send PUT request\ncurl -X PUT \\\n     -H \"Authorization: Bearer $USER_JWT\" \\\n     -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n     -d \"$PAYLOAD\" \\\n     \"$API_URL/channels/teams/tokens\"\n```"},"callProviderMetadata":{"vertex":{"thoughtSignature":"AY89a1+ayXLjCxum8165AbtXvJVjNgo6q2DOatQLMMFeVD7AcD/LeJe8wASZ7eUbRnNQ5kSxPKlPhdLytTJxtXinlYch4vKEnprPUmRHESD520fZfMVpVHtFnBt7sgFMlJtv5HoTHQ=="}}}}
